<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para><link linkend="_namespace_toolbox_1_1_core_1_1_services_1_1_cryptography">Cryptography</link> service implementation using AES symmetric encryption. </para>



<para>This service provides secure text encryption and decryption using the AES algorithm. It uses CBC mode with PKCS7 padding. </para>

<para>The encrypted output is Base64-encoded for safe text transmission. </para>

